title: Mini Car Racing
description:
Genre: Racing
Developer: AEON Design
Publisher: eGames

MINI CAR RACING is an all-new, unique racing game where you can create the ultimate speed machine and try your skill on more than 50 incredibly detailed 3D tracks. Collect money and upgrade your car with better tires, faster engines, power-ups and much more!

Features :

* Over 50 unique tracks!
* 8 different mini cars!
* Customise your car with cool graphics!
* 3 difficulty levels!
* 6 different playing modes!
* Play with up to 4 players!
* Incredible graphics and game play!
